                <head>257. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d257fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Council Institutional Files, 1977–1981, Box 112, <gloss
                            target="#t_SCC_1">SCC</gloss>–305, 4/23/80, Security Framework Follow
                        Up. Secret; Sensitive. The meeting took place in the White House Situation
                        Room. <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1">Carter</persName> wrote: “Zbig, J” at the
                        top of the page. The portion of the summary of conclusions on base
